<p><span class="anchor" id="p60"></span>حلف لَا رأى مُنْكرا<a href="#p60" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p61"></span>إِلَّا رَفعه إِلَى قَاضِي بر بِكُل قَاض<a href="#p61" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p62"></span>فِي ذَلِك الْبَلَد وَفِي غَيره<a href="#p62" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
